column5: Was there in july '97.Has anybody been there more recently, wondering if the place has changed at all.Thinking about giving it another try. Not to bad of a place,could of been cleaner. Largest northen was 42", but few and far between and all cookie cutter walleyes 13-15". What iritated me the most was that the owner was never there. Any replies would be apreciated.
Riley,Email me ragarding sportsmans. i have some info. for you.
